#: org.kde.sweeper.desktop:142
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Helps to clean unwanted traces the user leaves on the system and to regain "
"disk space removing unused temporary files"
msgstr ""
"Efaciar índesirat tracies quel un usator lassa in li sistema, e reganiar li "
"disc-spacie ocupat de ínusat temporari files"
